<p><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">在2023年的7月，身体不适的虞同学，在医院的检查中查出肌酐值的异常攀升，预示着肾功能衰竭已步入第五期的严峻阶段（尿毒症期）。随之而来的，是一系列复杂的疾病诊断：继发性甲状腺功能亢进、窦性心动过速，以及双侧甲状腺囊肿……<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">但是虞同学并没有选择退缩，而是以钢铁般的意志，毅然决然地踏上了漫长且荆棘密布的治疗之路。</span></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/20240709/1720490359314059318.jpg" title="1720490359314059318.jpg" alt="e4e34aaf0093c1ca2a0cb21ea65432d7.jpg" width="809" height="661" style="width: 809px; height: 661px;"/></span></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">时光如梭，2024年的春风带来了转机，他勇敢地迈过了“关键手术”这道坎。<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">2024年6月29日，一个原本应被阳光与欢笑填满的日子——江西软件职业技术大学井冈山校区的毕业典礼及学士学位授予仪式隆重举行，由于病魔缠身，让虞康琪无法亲临仪式现场。7月4日上午，江西软件职业技术大学的校领导与老师们，用他们独有的细腻与温情，决定打破常规，将这份迟到的荣誉与祝福，转化为一场独一无二的“毕业典礼”，直接送至虞康琪的家中。那一刻，家庭的温馨与学校的关怀交织成一幅动人的画卷，温暖了每一个人的心房。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;">举办了一场特殊的&#39;&#39;毕业典礼暨学位授予仪式‘’，这场仪式的主角是井冈山数字经济产业学院2024届&#39;&#39;信息安全与管理专业‘’学生虞康琪。<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0.544px;">学校“以人为本”的教育理念体现了教育的人文关怀，强调教育的根本目的是促进人的全面发展，使每个学生都能在学校找到适合自己的成长路径。这样的教育有助于培养适应未来社会需求的创新人才。</span></span></span><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">在这场特别的典礼上，每一个瞬间都凝聚着深情与关怀。当校长亲手为他拨正流苏的那一刹那，时间仿佛静止，所有的目光汇聚于这位勇敢的斗士身上。他的眼中，泪光闪烁，那是对往昔苦难的释怀，也是对未来希望的期盼。这一刻，他不再是孤军奋战的勇士，而是整个学校大家庭中不可或缺的一份子。这份独特的记忆，在时光的长河里，有些记忆仿佛是独一无二的宝藏，静静地沉淀在心底，成为我们生命中无法替代的唯美瞬间。</span></span></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/20240709/1720490396505072284.jpg" title="1720490396505072284.jpg" alt="7d4559c673a1dbad22ca83ddbd09844e.jpg" width="789" height="652" style="width: 789px; height: 652px;"/></span></span></span></p><p><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-indent: 2em; caret-color: rgb(5, 7, 59); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">这段经历，不仅是虞康琪个人的重生之旅，也是对人性光辉的深刻诠释。在此祝虞同学</span><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-indent: 2em; caret-color: rgb(5, 7, 59); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-weight: var(--cos-font-medium); font-family: -apple-system, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">愿你未来前程似锦，冬去春来，前无近忧，后无远虑。<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-weight: var(--cos-font-medium);">毕业不仅代表着结束，更是新生活的开始。<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-weight: var(--cos-font-medium);">愿你不断追求卓越，成就更加辉煌的未来。虞同学你要明白我们<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-weight: var(--cos-font-medium);">聚是一团火，散是满天星。<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-weight: var(--cos-font-medium);">愿你在自己的轨迹里，抬头时依旧满目星河，低头时道路万千。</span></span></span></span></span><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-indent: 2em; caret-color: rgb(5, 7, 59); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">多年来，学校坚持以生为本，把学生放在首位，“用心”“用情”“用爱”对待每一位学生。学校始终坚守教育初心，每一份细微的关怀之举都让学生感受到被重视、被关爱。这场特别的“毕业典礼”，不仅是对虞康琪同学不懈奋斗与坚韧精神的最高赞誉，更是江西软件职业技术大学“人文关怀与温暖教育”理念的生动展现。它让爱与希望战胜病痛，成为青春记忆中最灿烂的一页。愿虞康琪同学的每一天都充满阳光和欢笑，每一步都走得坚定而有力。在未来的日子里，愿你的梦想照进现实，希望变成幸福。</span></p><p><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-indent: 2em; caret-color: rgb(5, 7, 59); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/20240709/1720490250837082704.jpg" title="1720490250837082704.jpg" alt="b08b38fb3f12fef18323b51268293abc.jpg" width="781" height="599" style="width: 781px; height: 599px;"/></span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span></span><br/></p>